pgbadger -f stderr -j 4 /pg_logs/postgresql-23.log-20250724 -o /tmp/pgbadger_report.txt --outfile text

Finally, can run version
pgbadger -f stderr -j 4 --tempdir=/pg_backups/tmp /pg_logs/postgresql-23.log-20250724 -o /tmp/pgbadger_report.txt --outfile=text


